{"tid":1715703,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(又老屈) 國民黨 : 香港示威者潑酸, 傷及路過學生","createTime":"2019-11-13T07:03:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T01:59:37.000Z","uid":134071,"like":19,"dislike":194,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"e73d8b5d0bd3a6101f8278a52a13ae1a8992d726","tid":1715703,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:03:50.000Z","msg":"痂撚線? &nbsp;幾時有香港示威者潑酸, 傷及路過學生?  國民黨係平行時空?<br />\n<br />\n文章來自聯合報 (親國民黨媒體)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://udn.com/news/story/6656/4158449\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6656%2F4158449&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=2c466709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://udn.com/news/story/6656/4158449</a><br />\n<br />\n香港反送中衝突升高 國民黨：深感憂慮<br />\n2019-11-11 19:58聯合報 記者鄭媁／即時報導<br />\n<br />\n香港反送中引發警民衝突升級，今天有示威者中槍，情況危急。國民黨今表示，再次呼籲港府與示威民眾保持冷靜，以理性溝通建立良性互動，同時也企盼蔡政府拿出實際有效的方案，確保在港生活的台生、台商的人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n香港特首林鄭月娥傍晚會見媒體指出，好多網上流言謠傳，無中生有，完全不是事實的謠言，都是有企圖、有目的，呼籲廣大市民冷靜，看清楚事情，留意政府發出澄清公告。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>國民黨發言人黃心華表示，國民黨對於香港街頭抗爭活動越演越烈，甚至發生示威者潑酸傷及路過學生</strong>、以及警察開槍等流血事件，深感憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n黃心華指出，國民黨絕不樂見香港街頭暴力事件持續，亦不希望香港的社會秩序及港人的日常生活受到嚴重衝擊。國民黨再次呼籲大陸當局、港府及示威團體，能夠持續協商對話，共同找出讓社會回復穩定及恢復正常秩序的解方，也期盼香港能夠重新展現過往的經濟榮景，讓港民都能遠離矛盾及焦慮的心情，重拾安心生活、安居樂業。"},{"pid":"88fcb0a46fa34c79b0542ff25b729dfd8346e463","tid":1715703,"uid":134071,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣人不要投韓"},{"pid":"02ecb3344672831a195c8932287f0a19e90cfed2","tid":1715703,"uid":311004,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:05:02.000Z","msg":"又是老作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d986f5ebe51e19ed89ee09e6483f316bc9d3b06","tid":1715703,"uid":211914,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:05:42.000Z","msg":"叫成班撚樣落去同孫文講當年佢地起革命有幾撚唔啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb429b1f060770a85c9f8437582faa857267252","tid":1715703,"uid":212626,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:05:52.000Z","msg":"土共分支黨又老屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69502eb67c8ecc76b964b18245d50c238d0e9b2e","tid":1715703,"uid":36441,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:06:23.000Z","msg":"果然大家都係蘇聯扶植 國共一家親"},{"pid":"a86bbf5c39b0bf2f81aec15803c3173ba783ed45","tid":1715703,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"02ecb3344672831a195c8932287f0a19e90cfed2","tid":1715703,"uid":311004,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:05:02.000Z","msg":"又是老作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:06:51.000Z","msg":"國民黨政棍韓國瑜, 都成日老作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a4071032ae326f00ac5f3c2755922c5bbac40e","tid":1715703,"uid":198245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"69502eb67c8ecc76b964b18245d50c238d0e9b2e","tid":1715703,"uid":36441,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:06:23.000Z","msg":"果然大家都係蘇聯扶植 國共一家親"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:07:15.000Z","msg":"抵班仆街打輸俾共狗"},{"pid":"d246e1ea56220c73bdeca6f6b0147af89e225a58","tid":1715703,"uid":143284,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:07:56.000Z","msg":"今日呢班國民黨對唔對得住革命先賢？"},{"pid":"5542e1e271836c93ff5725b45adca1df3372ab41","tid":1715703,"uid":121255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:08:01.000Z","msg":"國喻黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929209d5ca6962883904009477ba38aff3c7564a","tid":1715703,"uid":311004,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:08:02.000Z","msg":"國民黨一定要清黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\